[2026-03-18T11:56:49.370Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01SrV3gTM94UzAWtv86o7zY5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 4 ideas saved successfully. Here's the summary:\n\n## Scan Complete: Tony Stark - Credential & Secret Management\n\n**4 ideas saved** to Vibeman (scan `52ba2374`):\n\n| # | Title | Category | Effort | Impact | Risk |\n|---|-------|----------|--------|--------|------|\n| 1 | **Envelope encryption with versioned key hierarchy** | functionality | 8 | 10 | 7 |\n| 2 | **JIT credential broker via Unix domain socket** | functionality | 8 | 9 | 7 |\n| 3 | **OS keystore-backed master key with DPAPI/Keychain** | performance | 7 | 9 | 8 |\n| 4 | **Isolated credential vault with sealed storage** | functionality | 9 | 9 | 8 |\n\n### Key observations from the codebase:\n\n- **No key rotation path**: The entire encryption chain derives from a single `MASTER_KEY` env var with a hardcoded PBKDF2 salt. Rotating the master requires re-encrypting every credential across all tenants simultaneously — operationally infeasible at scale.\n- **One-shot credential injection**: `credentialInjector.ts` writes all secrets to a temp file upfront. Workers can't refresh expiring OAuth tokens mid-execution, creating a hard ceiling for long-running personas.\n- **Master key lives as plaintext string**: Despite good buffer-zeroing hygiene in `TenantKeyManager`, the root `masterSecret` string persists in process memory for its entire lifetime.\n- **Credentials co-located with app data**: `persona_credentials` shares the same SQLite database as personas, events, and executions — no independent security boundary for secrets."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5369,"cache_read_input_tokens":56293,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5369},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b399cdad-908a-4da4-833a-66507675ad51","uuid":"b7d4e707-0f5b-4dfb-a180-312ae50218a8"}
